<A>__{roberta guaspari lives in east harlem with her daughter sofia, whom she adopted from el salvador. nick is a professional cellist in a graduate music program, and alexi has been accepted to medical school. roberta teaches violin to approximately 150 students a year in three east harlem elementary schools. the east harlem violin program, however, is still not funded by the new york city board of education. the money raised from fiddlefest supported roberta's violin program for three years. roberta and opus 118 continue their fundraising efforts to keep the program alive.}
